&lt;h2 style="text-align: center;"&gt;About our awesome company&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;Our goal is to deliver simple yet beautiful Free WordPress Themes so that you can finish with ease your next website project.&lt;/p&gt;
&amp;nbsp;

&lt;img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1159 img-responsive" src="http://envision-villa.cloudaccess.host/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/team.jpg" alt="team" width="1140" height="420" /&gt;

&amp;nbsp;
&lt;blockquote&gt;We like minimal design, not that it’s easy for us to achieve (well in fact it is), but our primary focus is your end-user, which will ultimately be the one who will interact with your website. We always keep it simple.&lt;/blockquote&gt;
EnvisonTheme, which is part of the Envision Group, was created solely to provide simple yet beautiful themes for the WordPress community. Our aim is that you may easily finish your website projects and to have additional time for yourself and for you family. Our designs are minimalist, focused only on the necessary elements.

Beside you, we think for your end-users as well, which will ultimately be the one that will interact with your website. Our aim for them is a simple and pleaant browsing experience.

